task.instruction: You are portfolio analyst Uriah Jenkins (uriahjenkins@hotmail.com) and need to update the end-of-day pricing for US Treasury 10Y bonds (UTY) for January 15, 2025. Today's pricing data shows: opening price $94.50, high price $95.25, low price $94.25, and closing price $94.75. After updating the complete pricing data, you want to analyze how this affects high-net-worth investors holding this bond and generate a comprehensive portfolio impact report for Patterson-Mendez (investor_id: 3), who has significant exposure to this instrument, send an email to the investor with the report. Can you help me update the bond price and assess the portfolio impact?
